# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  WhatsApp News Bot — Environment Variables
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── WHERE TO SEND NEWS ────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# You have 3 options — pick ONE:
#
# Option 1: Your personal WhatsApp number (with country code, no + or spaces)
#   Example: 919876543210
#
# Option 2: A WhatsApp Group name (must match exactly, case-insensitive)
#   Example: Cyber News Updates
#
# Option 3: A WhatsApp Group/Channel ID (most reliable, use list-groups.js to find it)
#   Example: 120363XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX@g.us
#
# HOW TO FIND YOUR GROUP ID:
#   1. First start the bot once and scan the QR code
#   2. Add the linked WhatsApp account to your group
#   3. Run: node list-groups.js
#   4. Copy the ID of your group and paste it below
#
WHATSAPP_TARGET=919XXXXXXXXX

# ── AI SUMMARIZATION (optional but recommended) ───────────────────
# Free Gemini API key from https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# If left blank, the bot still works using basic summarization
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
